Class Consumable

java.lang.Object
edu.monash.fit2099.engine.Item

Direct Known Subclasses:

public abstract class Consumable
extends PortableItem
Implements a consumable class that denotes all the items in game that are consumable to all types of dinosaurs
Version:
3.0.0
Author:
Tim Jordan, Enoch Leow
See Also:
PortableItem, Dinosaur, DinosaurCapabilities
